== Assizacho Bhagivont Francisk Achem Magnnem ==
'''Prayer of Saint Francis of Assisi'''


''Dhonia tuje xantichem hatiar Tum mhaka kor,''

''Zoim rag-dves zollta, thoim havem priti vompum;''

''zoim opman kortat thoim hanvem mafi korum,''

''zhoim dubhav rigla thoim hanvem bhavart thiravvum,''

''zhoim visvas bhongla thoim ami visvas pettom.''

''Zhoim kalluk poddla thoim hanvem uzvadd fankoum,''

''zhoim khont-dukh bhorlea thoim hanvem sontos vaddoum,''





''Eh ! Deivik Guruji, nirminakai hanvem mhakach bhuzvonn sodhunk,''

''punn hanvem dusreank bhuzvonn diunk,''

''nhoich mhakach som'zunk, punn hanvem dusreank som'zunk,'' 

''nhoich mhozoch mog korunk, punn dusreancho -i hanvem mog korunk,''

''kiteak jea mapanami dhi-in teach mapan ami ghein;''

''jea mapan ami dusreak bhogxim teach mapan amkam bhogsonnem melltelem,''

''ami dusream khatir morun sasnnachea jivitak ami porot zolmoteleanv.''



'''''Amen'''''

